---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read GraceSoft's Privacy Policy, including how personal data is collected, used, protected, and retained under Singapore PDPA principles."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <section
      class="title-section legal-hero relative isolate overflow-hidden text-white px-4 py-20 sm:py-24 lg:py-28"
    >
      <div
        class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-4 text-center reveal rise"
      >
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gs-purple-100 sm:text-base lg:text-xl">
          Last updated: March 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-content-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
        <div class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">
            GraceSoft ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is
            committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with the
            Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA) of Singapore.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">
            This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
            information when you visit our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            We only collect personal data that you voluntarily provide to us.
            This may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Any information you include in your message</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            This information is collected only when you contact us via our
            contact form or email.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information you provide solely to:</p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li>Respond to your enquiries</li>
            <li>Communicate with you regarding your request</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not use your data for marketing purposes without your consent.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal data to third parties.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your information may only be shared with trusted service providers
            (for example email or hosting services) where necessary to operate
            the website and respond to enquiries.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the
            purpose for which it was collected, or as required by applicable
            laws.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            GraceSoft does not use cookies or tracking technologies to collect
            personal data from visitors.
          </p>
          <p>
            If this changes in the future (for example analytics tools), this
            policy will be updated accordingly.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data from
            unauthorised access, disclosure, or misuse.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under the PDPA, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction of your personal data</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To do so, please contact our DPO at <a
              href="mailto:davinaleong@gracesoft.dev"
              class="legal-link">davinaleong@gracesoft.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>8. Data Protection Officer</h2>
          <p>
            GraceSoft has appointed a Data Protection Officer (DPO) to oversee
            compliance with the PDPA. If you have any questions or concerns
            about how your personal data is collected, used, or handled, you may
            contact our DPO directly:
          </p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li><strong>Name:</strong> Davina Leong</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Email:</strong>
              <a href="mailto:davinaleong@gracesoft.dev" class="legal-link"
                >davinaleong@gracesoft.dev</a>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +65 9122 4271</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data
            is handled, please contact our DPO at <a
              href="mailto:davinaleong@gracesoft.dev"
              class="legal-link">davinaleong@gracesoft.dev</a
            > or reach us at <a href="/contact" class="legal-link"
              >hello@gracesoft.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block reveal rise delay-1">
          <h2>10. Updates to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes
            will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
